abstract: Michael Phelps, preparing for his fifth Olympics, wins 100-meter butterfly race in Arena Pro Swim Series event.
lead_paragraph: Preparing for his fifth Olympics, the 30-year-old Phelps won a race in an Arena Pro Swim Series event in Austin, Tex.

headline.main: Michael Phelps Wins 100 Butterfly in Texas
